data.description: Welcome Home! Get in before the holidays "South Grove" in the heart of Beech Grove a great updated stone/brick ranch with full finished basement and oversized two car detached garage with workshop and extra storage areas. Large kitchen/dining room have been completely opened up with new cabinets and counter tops,built-in appliances,10x5ft. island, new lighting and flooring w/ accent wall. Three full baths, three/four bedrooms on main. Two bedrooms have been opened up to make large owners suite but could be converted back to two separate rooms. There is a large great room with a fireplace and attached all-seasons back porch that has a second laundry hook-up on the main. Laundry in basement w/washer/dryer. Large family room in basement that has been water proofed and finished. Large carpeted bonus room in basement could be an office or a playroom.New mechanicals, newer roof, windows and weather head. Lots of built-in storage. Immediate poss.
